1671e1935f67504e15d56a8f","tid":745917,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T09:58:47.000Z","msg":"固定嘅文言文係漢代先出現<br />\n因為當時有董仲舒嘅獨尊儒術，令天下文人都讀儒家經典<br />\n儒家經典便成為大家嘅共同語言<br />\n統一常用詞彙<br />\n所以先有文言文"},{"pid":"97236a16142a26ca992c1335f6a3f842b55f78da","tid":745917,"uid":191790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T10:01:26.000Z","msg":"白話<br />\n你話楚辭係白話詩都得<br />\n但係佢唔係大家嘅共同語言"},{"pid":"d16fb47238b8f91ca3793c1493fad3a424936b2e","tid":745917,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:29:46.000Z","msg":"以前，白話同文言文並存，兩套唔同系統。之後就提倡寫白話文，變成依家咁。"},{"pid":"87d6fb3214893a76ddf8d643116bc33a91844c8e","tid":745917,"uid":77646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:30:58.000Z","msg":"胡適"},{"pid":"0fd3302bb5dcfc712f0582aa361bd92c47eb683c","tid":745917,"uid":65736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T12:30:12.000Z","msg":"原來係咁 兩者原來係並存 thx巴打們<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}